167
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] naravno da uvijek ima puno odgovora.

168
00:15:52,340 --> 00:15:56,659
[SPEAKER_00] Može biti neki odgovor i dobar.

169
00:15:56,659 --> 00:16:01,799
[SPEAKER_00] Je li to baš uvijek trebamo prihvatiti?

170
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:06,080
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nam se nešto za neku situaciju treba riješiti,

171
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:08,220
[SPEAKER_00] dobili smo dobar odgovor.

172
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:11,240
[SPEAKER_00] Oćemo ga odmah prihvatiti?

173
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ga treba odmah prihvatiti?

174
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:15,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

175
00:16:15,399 --> 00:16:19,379
[SPEAKER_00] I tu vam je razlika malo kod poniznosti i bahatosti.

176
00:16:20,379 --> 00:16:26,679
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ponizni ljudi, ponizni ljudi teže najbolje, ne bolje.

177
00:16:26,679 --> 00:16:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] Teže najbolje.

178
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:32,840
