182
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:45,899
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to u životu težite.

183
00:16:45,899 --> 00:16:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] Tražite što je najbolje za vas.

184
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:49,240
