196
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto bi se zaustavio odmah na to?

197
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, evo, i to je dobro razmisli.

198
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:31,019
