00:21:48,940 --> 00:21:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] već u dijelima,

351
00:21:50,119 --> 00:21:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] u gestama.

352
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] Budi normalan.

353
00:21:52,740 --> 00:21:55,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad treba reagirati,

354
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] učiniti kao ovaj matematičar,

355
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:57,700
[SPEAKER_00] dobro dijelo,

356
00:21:57,700 --> 00:21:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] pokazati poniznosti,

357
00:21:59,519 --> 00:22:00,299
[SPEAKER_00] strpljivost,

358
00:22:00,299 --> 00:22:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] ljubav,

359
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:01,759
[SPEAKER_00] slušanje,

360
00:22:01,759 --> 00:22:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] ovo sve što sam nadeo,

361
00:22:03,119 --> 00:22:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] bravo.

362
00:22:04,099 --> 00:22:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] A to onda mora proizlaziti

363
00:22:06,500 --> 00:22:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] iste naše duhovnosti.

364
00:22:08,900 --> 00:22:10,140
[SPEAKER_00] Poniznost,

365
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:11,799
[SPEAKER_00] koja je konkretna,

366
00:22:12,099 --> 00:22:13,140
[SPEAKER_00] a ne falcifikat.

367
00:22:13,140 --> 00:22:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] I evo,

368
00:22:14,559 --> 00:22:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] neka nam ovaj

369
00:22:16,039 --> 00:22:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] antunovski hod,

370
00:22:17,059 --> 00:22:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] ovo gesto antunovskog hoda,

371
00:22:18,920 --> 00:22:20,740
[SPEAKER_00] zaista bude inspiracija

372
00:22:20,740 --> 00:22:22,759
[SPEAKER_00] da radimo na svojoj poniznosti,

373
00:22:22,759 --> 00:22:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer što možemo zadobiti,

374
00:22:25,380 --> 00:22:27,259
[SPEAKER_00] zadobit ćemo mudrost,

375
00:22:27,259 --> 00:22:28,799
[SPEAKER_00] koja nam je svima potrebna.

376
00:22:28,799 --> 00:22:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

